
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>AmicBridge — Borrow & Lend Marketplace</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: system-ui; margin: 0; padding: 28px; max-width: 960px; margin-inline: auto; }
      .card { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 16px; padding: 18px; margin-top: 14px; }
      .btnrow { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 12px; }
      a.btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-decoration: none; }
      a.primary { background: #111; color: #fff; border-color: #111; }
      .muted { color: #555; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>AmicBridge</h1>
    <p class="muted">A simple platform where borrowers request loans, lenders make offers, and a contract is generated when a deal is accepted.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>Start</h2>
      <div class="btnrow">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/borrow">I want to borrow</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/lend">I want to lend</a>
      </div>
      <p class="muted" style="margin-top:12px;">
        MVP note: No login, no payments, no KYC yet. This is the workflow skeleton.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Borrower submits a loan request.</li>
        <li>Lenders send offers (APR, fees, schedule).</li>
        <li>Borrower accepts an offer → deal is created.</li>
        <li>Contract page is generated (print / save as PDF).</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
